author: Giorgio Mendoza
description: The DE25-Standard development kit for the Altera University Program features the Intel Agilex 5 SoC FPGA with 138K logic elements, delivering up to 2.5× higher performance than previous generations. Combining high-performance FPGA fabric with an ARM-based hard processor system, it supports a broad range of digital logic, embedded systems, and robotics applications. The Agilex 5 […]
title: DE25-Standard Development Kit with Agilex 5 SoC FPGA and DDR4 Support
